{
  "texts": [
    "However, studies involving educators at the higher education level were not included. 5.",
    "These studies examined how PD programs enhance teachers' STEM literacy, self-confidence in classroom management, student engagement, instructional strategies, and overall teaching effectiveness.",
    "This was assessed using standardized methods or tools developed by researchers.",
    "Importantly, studies that solely evaluated collective teacher efficacy without a specific focus on STEM integration in classrooms were not part of this selection. 6.",
    "The study involved gathering essential quantitative and qualitative data."
  ]
}